    "description": "Handle the unique manual controls in the 3D action runner with spaceship flight simulation to continue your adventure and get more messages from the unknown. Avoid asteroids or fracture them with a plasma laser weapon! Beat Leaderboard! Battle the boss! And enjoy the chaos!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Keyboard Controls</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/83c9780f8527718fbc02510cf8450856.webp?t=1645341069\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/83c9780f8527718fbc02510cf8450856.poster.avif?t=1645341069\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=198 /></picture></span><br>Are designed to simulate the chaos of controlling a spaceship.<br>Each of the 4 colored zones is responsible for movement in a certain direction. Press different buttons in the colored zone to increase movement in a defined (shown by yellow arrows) direction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/085eec77e0cfa41d0528d52e7dfc9eb9.poster.avif?t=1645341069\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/085eec77e0cfa41d0528d52e7dfc9eb9.webm?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/085eec77e0cfa41d0528d52e7dfc9eb9.mp4?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The space is enormous - fly as long as you can and meet various gorgeous <i>spacescapes</i> along your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leaderboard</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/db8a1050f3dc2fea3eb38b1140770d1d.avif?t=1645341069\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br>Try your best on your way to the best pilots!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Main Menu</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/da7f6445b396574505ba70c29f87b9ab.poster.avif?t=1645341069\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/da7f6445b396574505ba70c29f87b9ab.webm?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/da7f6445b396574505ba70c29f87b9ab.mp4?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Look around and interact directly with screens, gauges, and other equipment of the spaceship cockpit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Campaign</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/95efc5f0e0f51b3cea90c785167d54dd.poster.avif?t=1645341069\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/95efc5f0e0f51b3cea90c785167d54dd.webm?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/95efc5f0e0f51b3cea90c785167d54dd.mp4?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This story begins with an unexpected encounter... An unknown messages you. Who is he and what are his motives? That's for you to decide.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plasma Laser Weapon</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/98016c67cf948fb66667f2512b14b98d.poster.avif?t=1645341069\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/98016c67cf948fb66667f2512b14b98d.webm?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/98016c67cf948fb66667f2512b14b98d.mp4?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To destroy the obstacles on your way to...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Boss</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/e7d847967b91dd3277f5a9a51da1f6c1.poster.avif?t=1645341069\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/e7d847967b91dd3277f5a9a51da1f6c1.webm?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/e7d847967b91dd3277f5a9a51da1f6c1.mp4?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A real challenge of your skill.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Energetic Music</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/4b9ac812d7105218324457c983d36bf9.poster.avif?t=1645341069\" width=112 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821410/extras/4b9ac812d7105218324457c983d36bf9.webm?t=1645341069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>At each level, you will be accompanied by a new vigorous soundtrack :3<br><br>Originally created in one week for the Brackeys Game Jam 2021.2 with the theme &quot;Let There Be Chaos&quot;. This version includes more content, visual improvements, and optimizations.",
